{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-lecture-template-tsx","path":"/lecture/DB/2025-01-16-동시성-제어(lock)/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h1 id=\"lock\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#lock\" aria-label=\"lock permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>lock</h1>\n<p>lock이라는 개념을 도입하여 동시성 제어를 구현하는 방법</p>\n<h2 id=\"write-lock\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#write-lock\" aria-label=\"write lock permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>write lock</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>데이터를 쓰려면 먼저 쓰려는 데이터에 대해 <code class=\"language-text\">write lock</code>을 획득해야 함</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">write lock</code>를 가지고 있는는 동안 다른 트랜잭션이 해당 데이터를 쓰지 못하도록 함</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"read-lock\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#read-lock\" aria-label=\"read lock permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>read lock</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>데이터를 읽으려면 먼저 읽으려는 데이터에 대해 <code class=\"language-text\">read lock</code>을 획득해야 함</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">read lock</code>를 가지고 있는 동안 다른 트랜잭션이 해당 데이터를 쓰지 못하지만, 읽을 수는 있음</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"read-lock-write-lock-조합\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#read-lock-write-lock-%EC%A1%B0%ED%95%A9\" aria-label=\"read lock write lock 조합 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>read lock, write lock 조합</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">lock</code>사용 예시시</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/209e8729-a88e-46f1-88d9-227fdf5e4269\" alt=\"Image\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">read lock</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">write lock</code> 조합</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/bbeef2aa-5167-4d0a-a687-2493df103469\" alt=\"Image\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"lock을-사용하여도-일어나는-이상-현상\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#lock%EC%9D%84-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EC%97%AC%EB%8F%84-%EC%9D%BC%EC%96%B4%EB%82%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%9D%B4%EC%83%81-%ED%98%84%EC%83%81\" aria-label=\"lock을 사용하여도 일어나는 이상 현상 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>lock을 사용하여도 일어나는 이상 현상</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>아래 예시의 <code class=\"language-text\">serial schedule #1</code>은 <code class=\"language-text\">t1</code> => <code class=\"language-text\">t2</code> 순서로 실행되었을 때 결과가\n<ul>\n<li>x 300</li>\n<li>y 500</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">serial schedule #2</code>는 <code class=\"language-text\">t2</code> => <code class=\"language-text\">t1</code> 순서로 실행되었을 때 결과가\n<ul>\n<li>x 400</li>\n<li>y 300</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>하지만 <code class=\"language-text\">lock</code>을 사용한 임의의 순서에 <code class=\"language-text\">schedule</code> 결과는\n<ul>\n<li>x 300</li>\n<li>y 300</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>즉, <code class=\"language-text\">lock</code>을 사용하여도 <code class=\"language-text\">non-serial schedule</code>가 발생할 수 있음</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b54609e2-f21b-45b9-b044-d3c9dee9124d\" alt=\"Image\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"2pl-protocoltwo-phase-locking-protocol\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2pl-protocoltwo-phase-locking-protocol\" aria-label=\"2pl protocoltwo phase locking protocol permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2PL protocol(Two-Phase Locking Protocol)</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>위의 문제를 해결하는 방법법</li>\n<li>모든 <code class=\"language-text\">lock operation</code>이 최초의 <code class=\"language-text\">unlock operation</code> 보다 먼저 수행되어야 함.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">serializability</code>를 보장함</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b26a0473-32ab-4874-a4c3-9764a8f64370\" alt=\"Image\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Expanding phase</code> : <code class=\"language-text\">lock</code>을 취득하고 반환하지 않는 phase</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Shrinking phase</code> : <code class=\"language-text\">lock</code>을 반환하고(<code class=\"language-text\">unlock</code>) 취득하지 않는 phase</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>2PL protocol에서는 OS의 데드락과 같은 문제가 발생할 수 있음<br>\n해결 방법 또한 OS의 데드락과 동일</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"다양한-종류의-2pl-protocol\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8B%A4%EC%96%91%ED%95%9C-%EC%A2%85%EB%A5%98%EC%9D%98-2pl-protocol\" aria-label=\"다양한 종류의 2pl protocol permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>다양한 종류의 2PL protocol</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>2PL protocol은 세부적인 방식에 따라 여러 종류가 있음</li>\n<li>다음 예시를 기준으로 설명</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/23650201-0df2-4d28-b6a9-780439e80c8b\" alt=\"Image\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"conservative-2pl-protocol\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#conservative-2pl-protocol\" aria-label=\"conservative 2pl protocol permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>conservative 2PL protocol</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>필요한 모든 <code class=\"language-text\">lock</code>을 취득하고 트랜잭션 진행</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">deadlock free</code></li>\n<li>모든 <code class=\"language-text\">lock</code>을 취득하는 것 자체가 실용적이지 않음음</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e6b6b16c-6af7-4fa8-aa65-1a8604320035\" alt=\"Image\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"strict-2pl-protocol\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#strict-2pl-protocol\" aria-label=\"strict 2pl protocol permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>strict 2PL protocol</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">strict schedule</code>을 보장하는 방법(<code class=\"language-text\">recoverability</code> 보장)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">write lock</code>을 커밋, 롤백 할 때 반환환</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/96532a4a-3043-40c7-84cc-2904280df0a4\" alt=\"Image\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"strong-strict-2pl-protocol\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#strong-strict-2pl-protocol\" aria-label=\"strong strict 2pl protocol permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>strong strict 2PL protocol</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">strict 2PL</code>와 동일</li>\n<li>추가로 <code class=\"language-text\">read lock</code> 또한 커밋, 롤백 할 때 반환함</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ed148937-0fbe-4e70-8d49-b9b0660a922e\" alt=\"Image\"></p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#lock\">lock</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#write-lock\">write lock</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#read-lock\">read lock</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#read-lock-write-lock-%EC%A1%B0%ED%95%A9\">read lock, write lock 조합</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#lock%EC%9D%84-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EC%97%AC%EB%8F%84-%EC%9D%BC%EC%96%B4%EB%82%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%9D%B4%EC%83%81-%ED%98%84%EC%83%81\">lock을 사용하여도 일어나는 이상 현상</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2pl-protocoltwo-phase-locking-protocol\">2PL protocol(Two-Phase Locking Protocol)</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EB%8B%A4%EC%96%91%ED%95%9C-%EC%A2%85%EB%A5%98%EC%9D%98-2pl-protocol\">다양한 종류의 2PL protocol</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#conservative-2pl-protocol\">conservative 2PL protocol</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#strict-2pl-protocol\">strict 2PL protocol</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#strong-strict-2pl-protocol\">strong strict 2PL protocol</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"동시성 제어(lock)","date":"2025년 01월 16일","tags":["CS"]}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/lecture/DB/2025-01-16-동시성-제어(lock)/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/lecture/DB/2025-01-15-transaction-isolation-level/"},"frontmatter":{"categories":["DB"],"title":"transaction isolation level","date":"2025-01-15 18:00:00 +0900","tags":["CS"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/lecture/DB/2025-01-17-MVCC/"},"frontmatter":{"categories":["DB"],"title":"MVCC","date":"2025-01-17 18:00:00 +0900","tags":["CS"]}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}